.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, white, yellow
There are 5 different nationalities: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: gospel, classical, ambient, rock, disco
House: craftsman, palace, futuristic, tower, gothic-revival
5 different pets are kept: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. the british is the person who likes red
2. the swedish is the owner of the dog
3. the danish is the fan of rock
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes white
5. the person who likes green is the fan of classical
6. the futuristic house is the owner of the bird
7. the person who likes yellow is the palace house
8. the fan of ambient is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the owner of the cat
11. the owner of the horses is on the left or right of the palace house
12. the craftsman house is the fan of gospel
13. the german is the tower house
14. the norwegian is on the left or right of the person who likes blue
15. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the fan of disco

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     cat	|    horse	|     bird	|     fish	|      dog	|
| Music-Genre	|    disco	|     rock	|     ambient	|    classical	|      gospel	|
| House		|   palace	|    gothic-revival	|  futuristic	|    tower	|   craftsman	|
